{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "personal_assistant - OJ 排行榜接口",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "仅覆盖 1 个接口：POST /oj/ranking_list。\n\n接口定位：\n- 该接口位于 BusinessGroup，下游会经过 JWTAuth 与 ActiveUserMW。\n- 不经过 PermissionMiddleware，但 Service 内部会按 scope 做权限校验。\n- 请求体为 JSON，Controller 当前使用 ShouldBindJSON 绑定。\n\n本次变更重点：\n- 请求体新增 scope 字段，支持 current_org / all_members / org 三种查询范围。\n- 请求体新增 org_id 字段，仅在 scope=org 时需要传入。\n- 响应体的数据结构 OJRankingListResp 未变化。\n\n当前实现注意事项：\n- 该接口的 Controller 仍使用旧版 Response 壳返回成功/业务失败：code + data + messages/error。\n- JWTAuth 中间件拦截未登录、Token 失效时，也返回旧版 Response 壳，HTTP 状态码为 200。\n- ActiveUserMW 拦截账号禁用时，返回新版 BizResponse，HTTP 状态码为 401。\n- 除 invalid platform 外，scope/org_id/组织成员校验失败等场景，当前 Controller 会统一返回 code=10004，并把具体错误文本放在 error 字段中。"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://127.0.0.1:9000",
      "description": "本地开发环境（请按实际地址修改）"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "OJ-排行榜",
      "description": "OJ 排行榜查询接口，支持当前组织、全体成员总榜、指定组织榜单。"
    }
  ],
  "security": [
    {
      "BearerAuth": []
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/oj/ranking_list": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "OJ-排行榜"
        ],
        "summary": "查询 OJ 排行榜",
        "description": "查询指定平台的排行榜。\n\nscope 说明：\n- current_org：查询当前组织榜单；默认值。\n- all_members：查询全体成员总榜。\n- org：查询指定 org_id 的组织榜单。\n\n权限规则：\n- 已登录且账号 active 的用户才能访问。\n- scope=all_members：任何已登录且 active 的用户都可以查询。\n- scope=current_org：查询当前组织；如果当前组织本身就是内置“全体成员”组织，则自动映射到总榜。\n- scope=org：\n  - 普通用户只能查询自己仍为 active 成员的组织；\n  - super_admin 可以查询任意组织。\n\n排序规则：\n- 排行榜基于 Redis ZSet 倒序返回，分数越高排名越靠前。\n- 当前实现分页参数仍使用 page/page_size，服务端会转换为 ZSet 范围查询。\n\n平台规则：\n- platform=luogu 时，platform_details.luogu 有值。\n- platform=leetcode 时，platform_details.leetcode 有值。",
        "operationId": "GetOJRankingList",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OJRankingListReq"
              },
              "examples": {
                "当前组织榜": {
                  "summary": "默认查询当前组织榜单",
                  "value": {
                    "page": 1,
                    "page_size": 20,
                    "platform": "luogu",
                    "scope": "current_org"
                  }
                },
                "全体成员总榜": {
                  "summary": "查询全体成员总榜",
                  "value": {
                    "page": 1,
                    "page_size": 20,
                    "platform": "leetcode",
                    "scope": "all_members"
                  }
                },
                "指定组织榜": {
                  "summary": "查询指定组织榜单",
                  "value": {
                    "page": 1,
                    "page_size": 20,
                    "platform": "luogu",
                    "scope": "org",
                    "org_id": 39
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功、业务失败、未登录或 Token 无效都可能返回 HTTP 200；请结合 code 与返回壳结构判断。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacySuccessResponseOJRankingList"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyErrorResponse"
                    },
                    {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LegacyAuthErrorResponse"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "examples": {
                  "查询成功-当前组织榜": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 0,
                      "data": {
                        "list": [
                          {
                            "rank": 1,
                            "user_id": 12,
                            "real_name": "alice",
                            "avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/alice.png",
                            "total_passed": 321,
                            "platform_details": {
                              "luogu": 321
                            }
                          },
                          {
                            "rank": 2,
                            "user_id": 18,
                            "real_name": "bob",
                            "avatar": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar/bob.png",
                            "total_passed": 287,
                            "platform_details": {
                              "luogu": 287
                            }
                          }
                        ],
                        "my_rank": {
                          "rank": 7,
                          "total_passed": 120
                        },
                        "total": 86
                      },
                      "messages": "获取成功"
                    }
                  },
                  "平台非法": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 40003,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "获取排行榜失败: invalid platform"
                    }
                  },
                  "scope为org但缺少org_id": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 10004,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "获取排行榜失败: org_id is required for org scope"
                    }
                  },
                  "无权查询指定组织": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 10004,
                      "data": null,
                      "error": "获取排行榜失败: user organization not active"
                    }
                  },
                  "未登录-缺少AccessToken": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 11005,
                      "data": {
                        "message": "Access token is required",
                        "reload": true
                      },
                      "error": "Access token is required"
                    }
                  },
                  "Token无效": {
                    "value": {
                      "code": 11003,
                      "data": {
                        "message": "Invalid access token",
                        "reload": true
                      },
                      "error": "Invalid access token"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "账号活跃态校验失败，例如账号已禁用。",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BizResponseUnauthorized"
                },
                "example": {
                  "code": 11000,
                  "success": false,
                  "message": "账号已禁用",
                  "data": null,
                  "timestamp": 1770850000001
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "BearerAuth": {
        "type": "http",
        "scheme": "bearer",
        "bearerFormat": "JWT",
        "description": "登录后在 Authorization 头中传入：Bearer <access_token>"
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "OJRankingListReq": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "OJ 排行榜查询请求体。",
        "properties": {
          "page": {
            "type": "integer",
            "minimum": 1,
            "default": 1,
            "description": "页码。服务端默认值为 1。"
          },
          "page_size": {
            "type": "integer",
            "minimum": 1,
            "maximum": 100,
            "default": 20,
            "description": "每页条数。服务端默认值为 20，最大 100。"
          },
          "platform": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "luogu",
              "leetcode"
            ],
            "description": "OJ 平台标识。luogu 表示洛谷，leetcode 表示力扣。"
          },
          "scope": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "current_org",
              "all_members",
              "org"
            ],
            "default": "current_org",
            "description": "排行榜范围。\n- current_org：当前组织榜单\n- all_members：全体成员总榜\n- org：指定组织榜单"
          },
          "org_id": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "uint64",
            "minimum": 1,
            "nullable": true,
            "description": "组织 ID。仅当 scope=org 时需要传入；其他 scope 下可省略。"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "platform"
        ]
      },
      "OJRankingListRespData": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "排行榜数据结构。该结构本次未变更。",
        "properties": {
          "list": {
            "type": "array",
            "description": "当前页排行榜列表。",
            "items": {
              "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OJRankingListItem"
            }
          },
          "my_rank": {
            "allOf": [
              {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OJRankingMyRank"
              }
            ],
            "nullable": true,
            "description": "当前登录用户在该榜单中的名次；如果未上榜则可能为 null。"
          },
          "total": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "description": "榜单总人数。"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "list",
          "total"
        ]
      },
      "OJRankingListItem": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "排行榜单条记录。",
        "properties": {
          "rank": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "当前页内换算后的真实排名，从 1 开始。"
          },
          "user_id": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "uint64",
            "description": "用户 ID。"
          },
          "real_name": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "展示名称。当前实现使用系统用户名。"
          },
          "avatar": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "展示头像。优先使用对应平台头像，缺失时回退到系统头像。"
          },
          "total_passed": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "该平台排行榜排序分值。洛谷为通过题数，力扣为总通过题数。"
          },
          "platform_details": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OJRankingPlatformDetails"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "rank",
          "user_id",
          "real_name",
          "avatar",
          "total_passed"
        ]
      },
      "OJRankingPlatformDetails": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "平台维度详情。当前只会返回与 platform 对应的一个字段。",
        "properties": {
          "luogu": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "洛谷通过题数。仅当 platform=luogu 时有值。"
          },
          "leetcode": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "力扣总通过题数。仅当 platform=leetcode 时有值。"
          }
        }
      },
      "OJRankingMyRank": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "当前登录用户在目标榜单中的名次信息。",
        "properties": {
          "rank": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "我的名次，从 1 开始。"
          },
          "total_passed": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "我的平台分值。"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "rank",
          "total_passed"
        ]
      },
      "LegacySuccessResponseOJRankingList": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "当前 Controller 成功响应壳。",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "enum": [
              0
            ],
            "description": "业务码。0 表示成功。"
          },
          "data": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OJRankingListRespData"
          },
          "messages": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "成功消息。当前实现固定为“获取成功”。"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "code",
          "data",
          "messages"
        ]
      },
      "LegacyErrorResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "当前 Controller 业务失败响应壳。",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "业务码。当前实现中 invalid platform 会返回 40003；其他大多数业务失败会返回 10004。"
          },
          "data": {
            "nullable": true,
            "description": "失败时通常为 null。"
          },
          "error": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "失败描述。当前实现通常会带上“获取排行榜失败: ...”前缀。"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "code",
          "data",
          "error"
        ]
      },
      "LegacyAuthErrorResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "JWTAuth 中间件拦截时返回的旧版认证失败响应壳。",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "enum": [
              11001,
              11003,
              11005
            ],
            "description": "认证相关业务码。11005=需要登录，11001=Token 已过期，11003=Token 无效。"
          },
          "data": {
            "$ref": "#/components/schemas/AuthReloadData"
          },
          "error": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "认证失败原因。"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "code",
          "data",
          "error"
        ]
      },
      "AuthReloadData": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "旧版认证失败返回体中的 data 结构。",
        "properties": {
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "认证失败原因。"
          },
          "reload": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "提示前端应重置状态并重新登录。"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "message",
          "reload"
        ]
      },
      "BizResponseUnauthorized": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "ActiveUserMW 拦截时返回的新版 BizResponse。",
        "properties": {
          "code": {
            "type": "integer",
            "enum": [
              11000
            ],
            "description": "未授权业务码。"
          },
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "enum": [
              false
            ],
            "description": "固定为 false。"
          },
          "message": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "未授权说明，例如“账号已禁用”。"
          },
          "data": {
            "nullable": true,
            "description": "当前中间件返回为 null。"
          },
          "timestamp": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "description": "服务端响应时间戳（毫秒）。"
          }
        },
        "required": [
          "code",
          "success",
          "message",
          "data",
          "timestamp"
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
